item.title: What Am I Doing in the Middle of the Revolution?
item.description: What Am I Doing in the Middle of a Revolution? is a 1972 Spaghetti Western comedy film.

item.title: Sonny and Jed
item.description: Sonny and Jed is a 1972 Italian Spaghetti Western film about a sheriff's relentless effort to stop a robber and his girlfriend. The film was directed by Sergio Corbucci and is noted for its music, scored by Ennio Morricone.

item.title: White Comanche
item.description: White Comanche or Comanche blanco or Rio Honcho is a 1968 paella western starring William Shatner in two roles.
